Entries.Name: Mad Families
Entries.Title: Mad Families
Entries.Description: Vacationing families must share a campsite and compete in an outrageous tournament. From the guys who brought you Joe Dirt and Joe Dirt 2: Beautiful Loser. Starring Charlie Sheen and Leah Remini.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: From the Joe-Dirty minds of David Spade and Fred Wolf comes another epic tale of courage, family and untold stupidity.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: From the Joe-Dirty minds of David Spade and Fred Wolf comes another epic tale of courage, family and untold stupidity.

Entries.Name: The Matrix
Entries.Title: The Matrix
Entries.Description: Keanu Reeves stars in an explosive sci-fi adventure about a man who comes to believe that his everyday world is the product of a computer-driven digital matrix that feeds on humans.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Wake up from your gooey hibernation pods and behold Keanu Reeves in the movie that changed action sci-fi forever.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Wake up from your gooey hibernation pods and behold Keanu Reeves in the movie that changed action sci-fi forever.

Entries.Name: The Matrix Reloaded
Entries.Title: The Matrix Reloaded
Entries.Description: Neo, Trinity & Morpheus lead revolt against Machine Army unleashing their arsenal of extraordinary skills & weaponry against systematic forces of repression & exploitation.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Neo, Trinity and Morpheus return in a stellar sequel that manages to top its physics-defying predecessor.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Neo, Trinity and Morpheus return in a stellar sequel that manages to top its physics-defying predecessor.

Entries.Name: The Matrix Revolutions
Entries.Title: The Matrix Revolutions
Entries.Description: Neo is trapped in limbo between reality & Matrix, while Zion, last human city, is attacked by hordes of machines.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: The epic third in the franchise sends us farther down the rabbit hole while keeping the mind-melting excitement of the original.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: The epic third in the franchise sends us farther down the rabbit hole while keeping the mind-melting excitement of the original.

Entries.Name: The Net
Entries.Title: The Net
Entries.Description: A freelance computer systems analyst is plunged into a web of corruption and murder when she stumbles onto a program she was never meant to see.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Remember when ordering pizza online was the stuff of sci-fi movies? Sandra Bullock does in this prescient thriller.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Remember when ordering pizza online was the stuff of sci-fi movies? Sandra Bullock does in this prescient thriller.

Entries.Name: Obsessed
Entries.Title: Obsessed
Entries.Description: In this edge-of-your-seat thriller a successful professional man with a beautiful wife finds his idyllic life threatened by a temp in his office who turns out to be a stalker.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Beyoncé isn't having any of Ali Larter's man-snatching schemes in this Fatal Attraction makeover.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Beyoncé isn't having any of Ali Larter's man-snatching schemes in this Fatal Attraction makeover.

Entries.Name: Panic Room
Entries.Title: Panic Room
Entries.Description: When her home is invaded by three armed robbers, a divorced woman and her young daughter hide in their specially designed "panic room" but end up in a deadly cat-and-mouse game anyway.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Jodie Foster and Kristen Stewart share the familial terror in David Fincher's perfectly paced claustrophobic thrill ride.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Jodie Foster and Kristen Stewart share the familial terror in David Fincher's perfectly paced claustrophobic thrill ride.

Entries.Name: Paprika
Entries.Title: Paprika
Entries.Description: When a machine that allows therapists to enter their patient's dreams is stolen, all hell breaks loose. Only a young female therapist can stop it: Paprika.

Entries.Name: Party Boat
Entries.Title: Party Boat
Entries.Description: Max has a secret crush on his BFF, Kiley. When Max finds out Kiley's boyfriend plans to propose, he vows to steal her heart with an epic rager. Stars Brett Davern, Katie Leclerc, Jay Mohr, Sung Kang.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: A super-highbrow affair on a posh yacht. Just kiddiiiing... A raunchy ship-show starring Jay Mohr and Sung Kang.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: A super-highbrow affair on a posh yacht. Just kiddiiiing... A raunchy ship-show starring Jay Mohr and Sung Kang.

Entries.Name: Point Break
Entries.Title: Point Break
Entries.Description: To nab a gang of bank robbers, brash young G-man Johnny Utah goes undercover to infiltrate a group of surfers.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Keanu goes undercover to wipe out POTUS-masked bandits in an adrenaline junkies wet dream.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Keanu goes undercover to wipe out POTUS-masked bandits in an adrenaline junkies wet dream.

Entries.Name: Reign Over Me
Entries.Title: Reign Over Me
Entries.Description: A man who lost his family in the 9/11 attack on New York City runs into his old college roommate. Rekindling the friendship is the one thing that appears able to help the man recover from his grief.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Adam Sandler delivers his best dramatic turn yet in a moving performance that keeps pace with the mighty Don Cheadle.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Adam Sandler delivers his best dramatic turn yet in a moving performance that keeps pace with the mighty Don Cheadle.

Entries.Name: The Remaining
Entries.Title: The Remaining
Entries.Description: A group of friends scramble to survive a Rapture-like phenomena.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Alexa Vega’s wedding gets totally ruined by the Rapture and then the real terror begins in a legit scary survival tale.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Alexa Vega’s wedding gets totally ruined by the Rapture and then the real terror begins in a legit scary survival tale.

Entries.Name: The River Murders
Entries.Title: The River Murders
Entries.Description: A homicide detective  Ray Liotta  while investigating a series of murders becomes the prime suspect when the FBI uncovers his close personal ties to all the victims.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: As a rogue detective in the foggy Pacific Northwest  Ray Liotta delivers an intense performance in this thriller.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: As a rogue detective in the foggy Pacific Northwest  Ray Liotta delivers an intense performance in this thriller.

Entries.Name: Robotech: The Shadow Chronicles
Entries.Title: Robotech: The Shadow Chronicles
Entries.Description: In the year 2044 AD, the human race has reached out to the stars through the miracle of ROBOTECHNOLOGY, but not without bringing intergalactic war upon the Earth itself.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: An award-winning extension of the legendary series that introduced Mecha anime to U.S. audiences.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: An award-winning extension of the legendary series that introduced Mecha anime to U.S. audiences.

Entries.Name: Roger Corman’s Operation Rogue
Entries.Title: Roger Corman’s Operation Rogue
Entries.Description: Deep in the jungles of Southeast Asia, a terrorist organization has stolen materials to create a dangerous chemical bomb.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: When terrorists get the ingredients for a dirty bomb, a fiery showdown ensues in Roger Corman’s on-brand actioner.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: When terrorists get the ingredients for a dirty bomb, a fiery showdown ensues in Roger Corman’s on-brand actioner.

Entries.Name: Secret Window
Entries.Title: Secret Window
Entries.Description: A writer is stalked at his remote lakeside cabin by a psychotic stranger seeking revenge for perceived plagiarism.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Johnny Depp battles writers block and axe-happy John Turturro in this tight, fever-pitched nightmare from Stephen King.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Johnny Depp battles writers block and axe-happy John Turturro in this tight, fever-pitched nightmare from Stephen King.

Entries.Name: Single White Female
Entries.Title: Single White Female
Entries.Description: A newly-single yuppie's new roommate acquires more than just a room. Stylish, adrenaline-laced thriller stars Bridget Fonda and Jennifer Jason Leigh.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: A whip-smart take on the stalker-from-hell genre emboldened by an inspired turn from Jennifer Jason Leigh.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: A whip-smart take on the stalker-from-hell genre emboldened by an inspired turn from Jennifer Jason Leigh.

Entries.Name: So I Married An Axe Murderer
Entries.Title: So I Married An Axe Murderer
Entries.Description: Mike Myers takes the lead in this rousing comedy thriller as a romantically-jaded performance artist who finally thinks he's met his match in beautiful butcher Nancy Travis.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Mike Myers co-stars with Mike Myers in a cult comedy that anticipates the schizoid delirium of Austin Powers.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Mike Myers co-stars with Mike Myers in a cult comedy that anticipates the schizoid delirium of Austin Powers.

Entries.Name: Spun
Entries.Title: Spun
Entries.Description: A college dropout becomes chauffeur and errand boy for a crazed crystal methadrine cook.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Jason Schwartzman breaks bad in a meth-fueled descent into darkness tweaked with black humor and unexpected cameos.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Jason Schwartzman breaks bad in a meth-fueled descent into darkness tweaked with black humor and unexpected cameos.

Entries.Name: Stan Lee’s Mutants, Monsters And Marvels
Entries.Title: Stan Lee’s Mutants, Monsters And Marvels
Entries.Description: Filmmaker/Comic Writer Kevin Smith interviews comic book legend Stan Lee about his life and work in comics.
Entries.WhyItCrackles: Uber-geek Kevin Smith meets his comic God.
Entries.WhyItCracklesHTML: Uber-geek Kevin Smith meets his comic God.
